10133,"uid":9710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"23歲仲咁戇鳩"},{"pid":"9e74ebf89dbb051d9ed99be1086485c0b0435c77","tid":410133,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"初戀啫巴打你人生重好撚長<br />\n唔好當呢啲人係你全部<br />\n休息排 重新出發啦"},{"pid":"273e5cdaf1c8a2335c076a5948ee7b7688ba0659","tid":410133,"uid":15194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 個半月</blockquote><br />\n用力屌鳩我啦 我想醒啊<br />\n係唔係暖男 就一定比人拋棄"},{"pid":"556cbcc9f46268d9eb64b9c9ed1119827d4d134b","tid":410133,"uid":15194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:33:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>23歲仲咁戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n23歲 世事我睇得化<br />\n愛情我睇唔化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d11bd6b32d590277bf23cecb41dab5cb961a13","tid":410133,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5124ab8381d346bbffd8760d50acbaf9c631c511","tid":410133,"uid":31381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T09:38:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個半月 <br />\n睇黎你落左好多感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來我暪住佢 親手縫咗隻 公仔聖誕節特別送比佢<br />\n整成幾個星期 依加隻嘢 冇咗主人</blockquote><br />\n咪傻啦<br />\n先第一次<br />\n仲要個半月<br />\n我三年啦 無諗過要咩跳海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時間會沖淡一切 你而家度日如年 我明白<br />\n但過左幾個星期 你就會好返<br />\n最好搵下朋友去玩下 尻行又好 好過自己狂諗<br />\n到最後 就要檢討係邊度出現問題"}]}